text: This transmits obsolete IRM 4.76.20, Exempt Organizations Examinations Guidelines, Local Benevolent Life Insurance Associations, Mutual Ditch or Irrigation Companies, Mutual or Telephone or Electric Companies, and Like Organizations - IRC 501(c)(12).

This material is obsolete, having undergone a conversion to an audit technique guide. You can ﬁnd the guide in the Educational Resources and Guidance for Exempt Organizations at https://www.irs. gov/charities-non-proﬁts/educational-resources-and-guidance-for-exempt-organizations.
The IRM 4.76.20 dated December 1, 2006 is obsolete.
